snippet.textDisplay:
I don't think I have ever had a white/silver/black car...
Current: 2017 Subaru Crosstrek (orange)
Previous: 2008 Chevy Cobalt (Blue)
Previous: 1995ish: Kia Sephia (Maroon)
(These 3 where all bought close to new, from dealers. though I think the Cobalt and Kia I got a bit of discount on, as they were previous year models...)
Previous: used Red Toyota (maybe?)
Previous: OK, I have owned a silver car. I had a silver Chevy of some sort in here. bought used in late 1980s during college. Stored in Mom's garage (southern Illinois) from Mid 1991-early 93.
Before that was a green Volvo, and a green MG Midget. (Those two were courtesy of my Dad, who has always bought cars and rebuilt them..)
So, 1 silver car, in over 35 years of car ownership...
